Use the standard library
This is how to find_max of words:
   Remember that best is item 0 in words
   Remember that bests is tostring of best
   Remember that n is words's length
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that w is item i in words
      Remember that ws is tostring of w
      When ws is more than bests, then:
         Remember that best is w
         Remember that bests is ws
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is best
